#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid "Installing vmelilo"
msgstr "Yn sefydlu vmelilo"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid "Installing vmelilo boot loader"
msgstr "Yn sefydlu'r bŵtlwythydd vmelilo"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid "vmelilo installation failed.  Continue anyway?"
msgstr "Methodd sefydliad vmelilo. Mynd ymlaen fodd bynnag?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid ""
"The vmelilo package failed to install into /target/.  Installing vmelilo as "
"a boot loader is a required step.  The install problem might however be "
"unrelated to vmelilo, so continuing the installation may be possible."
msgstr ""
"Methodd y pecyn vmelilo sefydlu yn /target/. Mae sefydlu vmelilo fel "
"bŵtlwythydd yn gam angenrheidiol. Fodd bynnag, mae'n bosib nad yw'r broblem "
"sefydlu yn gysylltiedig a vmelilo, felly gall fod yn bosib mynd ymlaen â'r "
"sefydliad."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:19
msgid "Looking for root partition..."
msgstr "Yn chwilio am rhaniad gwraidd..."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:23
msgid "No root partition found"
msgstr "Dim rhaniad gwraidd wedi ei ganfod"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:23
msgid ""
"No partition is mounted as your new root partition. You must mount a root "
"partition first."
msgstr ""
"Does dim rhaniad wedi ei glymu fel eich rhaniad gwraidd newydd. Rhaid i chi "
"glymu rhaniad gwraidd yn gyntaf."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:29
msgid "Creating vmelilo configuration..."
msgstr "Yn creu cyfluniad vmelilo..."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "Failed to create vmelilo configuration"
msgstr "Methwyd creu cyfluniad vmelilo"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "The creation of the vmelilo configuration file failed."
msgstr "Methodd cread ffeil cyfluniad vmelilo."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:42
msgid "Installing vmelilo into bootstrap partition..."
msgstr "Yn sefydlu vmelilo i rhaniad bootstrap..."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:46
msgid "Failed to install bootloader"
msgstr "Methwyd sefydlu bŵtwlwythydd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:46
msgid "The installation of the vmelilo boot loader failed."
msgstr "Methodd sefydliad y bŵtlwythydd vmelilo."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:46
msgid "Please check the system log or the output on the third console (tty3)."
msgstr "Gwiriwch cofnod y system neu'r allbwn ar y trydydd consol (tty3)."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:46
msgid "Warning: Your system may be unbootable!"
msgstr "Rhybudd: Efallai ni ellir bŵtio eich system!"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Main menu item
#: ../templates:56
msgid "Install the vmelilo boot loader on a hard disk"
msgstr "Sefydlu'r bŵtlwythydd vmelilo ar ddisgen caled"
